    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Artists who specialize in bookworks, which are art works that exploit the book form or alter its physical structure as part of the content of the work.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
